{"tid":508093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台羅啟新涉酒駕被捕","createTime":"2017-12-24T02:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T05:22:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bd85d33943a0d4cf07dde0c7a0681b428101d02d","tid":508093,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T02:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20171224/s00046/2d589d5ec2f88fea61e580c7aac522f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20171224%2Fs00046%2F2d589d5ec2f88fea61e580c7aac522f8.jpg&h=d63890ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】前唱片騎師（DJ）羅啟新涉嫌酒後駕駛被捕。警方證實，昨早約11時東九龍總區交通部執行及管制組在觀塘觀塘道進行代號「QUICKCHASER」打擊酒後駕駛行動，其間共向19名司機做隨機呼氣測試，其中一名52歲姓羅男子未能通過酒精呼氣測試，涉嫌酒後駕駛被捕。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，被捕52歲姓羅男子為港台第二台前節目主持及監製，現任職香港電台電視部高級節目主任羅啟新；當時羅駕私家車沿觀塘道往旺角駛至apm對開，遇到警方設置的路障截查，羅被要求做酒精呼氣測試，結果顯示體內酒精含量超標近1倍，涉嫌酒後駕駛被捕帶署，至昨下午獲准保釋離去。本報記者昨晚就事件致電羅啟新，至截稿前未獲回應。"},{"pid":"9ac26e796c22ad96848ebc73816a5a7c8e5b0378","tid":508093,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T02:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a521b179a34377a552f9e0fde0d56b73fec09519","tid":508093,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b773301c3208bad2cff990d22d3485c03b6ade2f","tid":508093,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T05:18:50.000Z","msg":"頭條新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c22300ca9636d1a4c0b707436268c432740f9a6","tid":508093,"uid":55043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T05:22:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭條新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果三條友都係泛民打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}